{
  "stem": "11998.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while you're in camp, you sort of organize yourself so that you-- you had better uniform, and you had a sweater, or-- or an undershirt, or good underwear and socks, and-- and shoes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You organize all of that from-- from with-- from with-- within the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever-- whenever there's an exchange, you make sure that you get the best possible clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or you-- you took-- they gave us cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Cigarettes became money, so you could trade cigarettes for-- with the-- with the guy that was looking after giving out the-- the clothing, and the-- give him a bribe so that you could exchange better-- for better clothes.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had good clothes going-- before I went to the infirmary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But once you come out of the infirmary, they sent you back to the site.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You start from nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You start-- you go-- they remove everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You go to delousing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They give you new issue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you got the worst thing-- paper-thin uniforms and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I didn't want to leave that infirmary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So during the day, I would go into the-- into the infirmary-- the kitchen-- the-- we had our own kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I would help the guys to clean the dishes and deliver stuff to the people who could-- who were bedridden, who could not get out of bed, and tried to make myself useful.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Became in the evening, my foot was swollen up, and Zambromski says to me, Leipciger, you're not staying off that foot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, I'm going to give you one more week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it's not healed, you're going to go out on the-- the-- on the Baustelle anyways.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He knew exactly what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told me I have one more week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So sure enough, I stayed off my foot.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
